
STEPS TO MAKE AN IMAGE FROM A PDB 
#####  

Biopython --- > READ PDB

-> extract X,Y,Z

##### Input file

--> Orientation: Projection direction

Quaternions

--> Define I(x,y)--> image matrix

Pixel size
Box size 

--> Translate center of mass to 0,0,0 

#### Rotate along the direction of quaternions

--> Rotation Matrix

Rotate Structure.

### Project
 
--> Consider Gaussians at the atoms (sigma atom-dependent)
TIME it

--> Log -.... o spheres. 

### In the future --> Im proj  + CTF 
-- defocus --

#### RESULTS --- IMAGE CAL ###

